          <div class="text-[11px] uppercase tracking-[0.1em] text-text-muted mb-4 font-medium font-mono">FAQ</div>
          <h2 class="text-[clamp(18px,2vw,24px)] font-semibold text-text-primary leading-tight tracking-tight mb-6">Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
          <p class="text-[13px] text-text-secondary leading-relaxed mb-8 max-w-[420px]">
